title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You have more support in the form of friends or unseen cosmic assistance than you realize today. Perhaps youre inclined to avoid tackling a difficult situation, but it behooves you to give it a shot anyway. However, the real work of building your confidence may require you to leap into situations where you might lose footing. Your ambitious strategy is possibly counterintuitive but playing it safe often just leaves you playing in the comfort of your own backyard. Theodore Roosevelt wrote, Each time we face our fear, we gain strength, courage, and confidence in the doing. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
